          },
          "image": {},
          "text": {
            "format": 1,
            "content": "<p>Metanthropes is a brand <strong>new d100-based, setting-flexible game system</strong> with <strong>classless leveling</strong> where players develop <strong>Metapowers</strong> which empower them with unique, metaphysical gifts that transform them into something extraordinary.</p><p></p><img src=\"systems/metanthropes/artwork/ui/cover/metanthropes.png\" class=\" centered\" /><p style=\"text-align:center\"></p>",
            "markdown": ""
          },
