        {
          "sort": 378125,
          "name": "Premium Content for Foundry VTT",
          "type": "text",
          "_id": "PVX603XcfLXOOLKT",
          "title": {
            "show": true,
            "level": 1
          },
          "image": {},
          "text": {
            "format": 1,
            "content": "<p>Following <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/legitamine/metanthropes-introductory-zine\">our first KickStarter</a>, we are ramping up development of our Premium Content for Foundry VTT.</p><p></p><p>We are very excited to announce that we will be providing <strong>all KickStarter backers with their activation keys by the end of May 2024!</strong></p><p></p><p>If you missed out on our first KickStarter, you can now find <strong>Metanthropes Premium Content for Foundry VTT </strong><a href=\"https://metanthropes.com/store\"><strong>available for purchase on our website</strong></a><strong>!</strong></p><p></p><p>We are currently offering 3 Premium Modules for Foundry VTT:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Metanthropes: Introductory</strong> is a one-shot story with an amazing Opera map, premade Actors &amp; Journals, to help new players learn how to play the game and to introduce them to the setting of Metanthropes. This module is expected to be <strong>out of Early Access by July 2024.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Metanthropes: Core</strong> is the way the game is meant to be played, allowing for Character progression &amp; providing access to over 500 unique abilities for your Protagonists. This module is expected to be <strong>out of Early Access later in 2024.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Metanthropes: Homebrew</strong> allows you to tinker with the game rules, customize the Core content to your liking &amp; create your own. This module is expected to be <strong>out of Early Access by the end of 2024.</strong></p></li></ul><p></p><p>If you would be interested to support us during this early stage of development, we kindly offer a <strong>20% discount to all Early Access products</strong> &amp; you can also take advantage of our <strong>bundled offerings for additional discounts!</strong></p>"
          },
